snippet.title: HOW OVERPOWERED IS THE HIGHEST LEVEL NUCLEAR YORG.IO BASE? (99999+ GEMS PER SECOND) l Yorg.io Update
snippet.description:
HOW OVERPOWERED IS THE HIGHEST LEVEL NUCLEAR YORG.IO BASE? In today's episode we play Yorg.io! We try to hit the highest base evolution! The higher your base level, the stronger you weapons! I never made use of the Uranium in the server! With the uranium you can make nuclear weapons. Lets build factories, diamond miners, Cannons and turrets. In order to protect are self from the zombies! Can we hit 500 LIKES?!?!
